```js
// ❌ Current: tech stack exposed, no defensive headers
const app = express();
```

**Fix:** Use `helmet` (the standard Express hardening library):

```js
// ✅ Install: npm install helmet
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.use(helmet()); // Sets ~14 security headers at once, removes X-Powered-By

