---

#### 7. **No Body Parsing or Request Size Limits (OWASP A04)**

There is no `express.json()` or `express.urlencoded()` middleware. If POST/PUT routes are added later (very likely), the app will be silently vulnerable to missing input validation. Additionally, no request body size limit is set, enabling large-payload DoS attacks.

**Fix:** Add body parsing with size limits upfront:

